description: Living by their slogan “Simple food, made great. Just a little OffBeat,” the culinary masterz of Offbeat Eatz have transformed ordinary appetizers, burgers, and pizza into Premium Appetizerz, Artisan Burgerz, and Artisan Pizzaz; hence why Houstonians are huge fanz. Their menu features extraordinary eatz like Phuket Campeche (Texas wild caught shrimp lightly poached in Thai spices, finished in Thai spiced tomato sauce), the Soft-shell Crab Burger (Deep Fried Jumbo Soft-shell Crab topped with lettuce, tomato, and sriracha cream sauce), Garlic White Chicken Pizza (with white sauce, shredded roast chicken, roasted garlic, and fresh lemon juice), and so much more. You can’t help but feel lucky when you discover this eye-popping purple truck roaming the streets, serving up tasty and offbeat treats.
name: OffBeat Eatz
